name: Kurokodairu
description:
"They call this the hour of the kurokodairu. She waits patiently as the sun slowly sets on the horizon. A shadow covers her as something moves behind, but she pays it no mind.  It’s now her turn!" - Sykcolo / AI

Kurokodairu by @Sykcoloart

Taking something that most would consider ugly or repulsive and showing it in a different way that transforms it into something uniquely beautiful is the main passion behind this project that I called Metamorphoses.

This artwork is created using generative techniques to mutate and deconstruct a micrograph of reptile skin. 

Learn about the inspiration, story and techniques behind this project on my website: https://www.sykcolo.com/blog-1/the-metamorphoses-collection
